OL,3,CUnstable council finances in need of
OL,4,Cswift reform, spending watchdog warns
OL,6,FCouncil finances are increasingly
OL,7,Funsustainable and in need of reform,
OL,8,Fthe public spending watchdog has
OL,9,Fwarned.
OL,11,FThe National Audit Office (NAO) warned
OL,12,Ftown halls are becoming more and more
OL,13,Fpreoccupied by frontline services,
OL,14,Fwhile preventative measures are
OL,15,Fgetting less cash.
OL,17,FIn a report diving into local
OL,18,Fgovernment finances, the watchdog
OL,19,Facknowledged funding available to
OL,20,Fcouncils had increased by 4% over the
OL,21,Flast decade to #55.7 billion.
