OL,6,FBut funding per person has decreased
OL,7,Fover the same period since 2015 by 1%,
OL,8,Fand demand for services like adult and
OL,9,Fchild social care, temporary
OL,10,Faccommodation, and special educational
OL,11,Fneeds and disabilities has increased
OL,12,Fmore than the amount of new cash made
OL,13,Favailable.
OL,15,FPeople are also finding it more
OL,16,Fdifficult to access local services and
OL,17,Fwhen they do their needs are not well
OL,18,Fmet, the NAO report ` entitled "Local
OL,19,FGovernment Financial Stability" ` said.
