OL,3,CUnstable council finances in need of
OL,4,Cswift reform, spending watchdog warns
OL,6,FMinisters must develop a plan aimed at
OL,7,Freforming funding and services which
OL,8,Fwill address the financial and demand
OL,9,Fpressures councils are facing, the
OL,10,Fwatchdog recommended.
OL,12,FIt also called on the Ministry of
OL,13,FHousing, Communities, and Local
OL,14,FGovernment to work with the Treasury
OL,15,Fon bolstering preventative programmes,
OL,16,Fto stop the most in-demand public
OL,17,Fservices from being overwhelmed.
