OL,3,CUnstable council finances in need of
OL,4,Cswift reform, spending watchdog warns
OL,6,FGareth Davies, head of the NAO, said:
OL,7,F"There have been repeated delays to
OL,8,Flocal government finance reform and
OL,9,FGovernment can no longer resort to
OL,10,Fshort-term solutions to support local
OL,11,Fauthorities.
OL,13,F"Action to address this must resolve
OL,14,Fthe systemic weaknesses in local
OL,15,Fgovernment financial sustainability
OL,16,Fthrough a comprehensive, cross-
OL,17,FGovernment approach."
