OL,3,CUnstable council finances in need of
OL,4,Cswift reform, spending watchdog warns
OL,6,F"The NAO rightly highlights that
OL,7,Ffunding pressures are being
OL,8,Fexacerbated by a lack of reform which
OL,9,Fhas weakened the financial
OL,10,Fsustainability of councils and left
OL,11,Fthem with a complex, outdated funding
OL,12,Fsystem.
OL,14,F"Creating an improved and a more
OL,15,Fsustainable funding system for local
OL,16,Fgovernment is also critical to
OL,17,Fstrengthen the value for money of
OL,18,Flocal spending and, most importantly,
OL,19,Fimprove services for communities."
