OL,3,CUnstable council finances in need of
OL,4,Cswift reform, spending watchdog warns
OL,6,FTim Oliver, chair of the County
OL,7,FCouncils Network, said: "As this NAO
OL,8,Freport shows, it is market-specific
OL,9,Fcost pressures, mainly in adult social
OL,10,Fcare, children' services, and special
OL,11,Feducational needs, that are driving
OL,12,Fcouncils' costs rather than
OL,13,Fdeprivation.
OL,15,F"Therefore, Government must recognise
OL,16,Fand address these pressures in its
OL,17,Ffair funding review, otherwise it will
OL,18,Fpush many well-run councils to the
OL,19,Fbrink."
